Description:
Create a &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#edc63e"&gt;5m&lt;/font&gt; radius storm at the target area that deals &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#edc63e"&gt;{[0.170000 * 100]}%&lt;/font&gt; &lt;img src="lyshineui/images/icons/tooltip/icon_tooltip_ice_opaque" xPadding="4" scale="1.7" yOffset="4"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;weapon damage every &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#edc63e"&gt;{[0.330000]}s&lt;/font&gt; for &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#edc63e"&gt;5s&lt;/font&gt;. The storm also creates a &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#edc63e"&gt;frosted area&lt;/font&gt; that slows enemies in it by &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#edc63e"&gt;{[-0.250000 * -100]}%&lt;/font&gt;. &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_Regular_Italic.font" color="#828282"&gt;(Slow reduces target's movement speed.)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_Regular_Italic.font" color="#828282"&gt;

(This effect cannot be dispelled.)&lt;/font&gt;

Cost &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#edc63e"&gt;{[25.000000]}&lt;/font&gt; mana.

Blasts a column of freezing winds forward that &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#edc63e"&gt;pushes&lt;/font&gt; back enemies &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#edc63e"&gt;5m&lt;/font&gt; and deals &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#edc63e"&gt;{[0.240000 * 100]}%&lt;/font&gt; &lt;img src="lyshineui/images/icons/tooltip/icon_tooltip_ice_opaque" xPadding="4" scale="1.7" yOffset="4"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;weapon damage every &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#edc63e"&gt;0.2s&lt;/font&gt; for &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#edc63e"&gt;2s&lt;/font&gt;. Wind Chill has a total range of &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#edc63e"&gt;7m&lt;/font&gt; with the farthest &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#edc63e"&gt;2m&lt;/font&gt; increasing damage &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#edc63e"&gt;25%&lt;/font&gt; without pushing enemies.&lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_Regular_Italic.font" color="#828282"&gt;

This ability has &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#edc63e"&gt;grit&lt;/font&gt;. &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_Regular_Italic.font" color="#828282"&gt;(Grit prevents you from being staggered by incoming attacks.)&lt;/font&gt;

(Player is able to move during the attack.)&lt;/font&gt;

Cost &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#edc63e"&gt;{[20.000000]}&lt;/font&gt; mana.&lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_Regular_Italic.font" color="#828282"&gt;

Taunt Gem Compatible: If you have a Carnelian gem equipped in your ice gauntlet, hits with this ability inflict taunt for {[3.000000]}s. (Taunt causes monsters to focus only on you.)&lt;/font&gt;

Summon a shower of ice that creates a &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#edc63e"&gt;frosted area&lt;/font&gt; approximately &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#edc63e"&gt;1m by 5m&lt;/font&gt; that lasts for &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#edc63e"&gt;4s&lt;/font&gt;. Enemies that enter the Ice Shower will be stricken with a powerful &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#edc63e"&gt;frostbite&lt;/font&gt;.

Frostbite &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#edc63e"&gt;roots&lt;/font&gt; for &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#edc63e"&gt;{[1.000000]}s&lt;/font&gt;, &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#edc63e"&gt;slows&lt;/font&gt; movement speed by &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#edc63e"&gt;{[-0.500000 * -100]}%&lt;/font&gt;, and will remain on target for &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#edc63e"&gt;{[3.000000]}s&lt;/font&gt; after exiting the Ice Shower. &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_Regular_Italic.font" color="#828282"&gt;(Ice Shower's root can only be applied once every {[6.000000]}s to the same target.)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_Regular_Italic.font" color="#828282"&gt;

(This effect cannot be dispelled.)&lt;/font&gt;

Cost &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#edc63e"&gt;{[25.000000]}&lt;/font&gt; mana.
